title: Kendall Jenner bares bum for Mario Testino V magazine cover as she reveals battle with anxiety
text:
Celebs Kendall Jenner bares bum for Mario Testino V magazine cover as she reveals battle with anxiety The model, 21, admitted that she's been struggling with the debilitating condition and "security concerns" have made it worse Share Kendall admitted to struggling with anxiety (Photo: FameFlynet) Share Get celebs   Could   
Kendall Jenner debuted a huge snake tattoo for her latest magazine cover shoot. 
But mum Kris Jenner needn't freak out just yet - it's all for the cameras. 
The 21-year-old model bared her bum for the January issue of V Magazine, shot by world renowned photographer, Mario Testino. 
Proud Kris shared the snap on Instagram, writing: "Absolutely stunning, Kendall!!! @Vmagazineâ€™s January issue! Shot by @mariotestino, on newsstands Jan 12. #proudmama #mybeauty #vmagazine" Read More (Photo: V Magazine) 
Kendall recently revealed that she has been suffering with anxiety. 
The reality TV star admitted that she has been struggling with the debilitating condition and "security concerns" have made it worse. 
Writing on her website KendallJ.com, she said: "Anxiety was a huge hurdle for me to deal with this past year (and security concerns didn't help), but I think I'm finally learning how to cope." 
The entire Kardashian/Jenner family have stepped up their security after Kim Kardashian West was robbed at gunpoint in her Paris hotel room last year. Read More Kim broke her social media silence to share a pic with her mum (Photo: Snapchat/Kim Kardashian) Kim also shared a sweet snap of son Saint (Photo: Instagram/kimkardashian) 
Kendall also admitted that she desperately misses her family and friends when she is away from home for work. 
She said: "The hardest part about my job is being away from home so often. I miss my sisters, the rest of my family and my friends so much when I'm away. But, it makes the time we have together that much more special." Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
